<br>
Quite frankly I'm really tired of it.  It seems to be the same few mods that are doing it over and over again. <br>
I don't believe these one or two individuals should have control over the voice of The Nameless.  <br>
Yes its their board, yes their the mods, but from my understanding didn't alot of different people donate to get this board up and running?  I may be mistaken.<br>
<br>
I for one would be willing to donate some money if other members would do the same, to see a new board opened up.    I for one do not have the time in RL, or the necessary knowledge to set up an EZboard, or moderate it.  Someone would have to step up and set up the board, and NOT moderate it... <br>
<br>
If I donate my hard earned cash, I would ask that the only moderation on the board be to move a post that turned into a rant, from general to a rants and flames column for example.     I don't want to see people's posts edited, modified, locked or deleted.  I want a freespeech forum.  <br>
<br>
JP<br>
