<br>
When you 'donate' to a cause, you give monies or items to that cause to support it.  You don't get a say in how it operates.  When you 'invest' in a cause you get a say in how it operates.  All these people donated.<br>
<br>
Just wanted to make that distinction. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
