I don't recall how much it would take to get over the 30 bucks for 6 months, but when this board was up for Gold last time, I think it was initially like $600 to get Gold for 6 months.  Barn started a campain to raise the money and lower the cost.  Forums got locked until the amount was raised.  It was pure hell.<br>
<br>
One thing I'll point out.  Back then we weren't allowed to have sigs because a lot of people made them too big and some didn't like them at all.  When it came time to raise the money, people said they'd donate only when we get the usage of sigs back.<br>
<br>
If I remember right, I think the 6 months is coming up soon and that might be a driving factor in the heavier moderation lately.  But half the fun in R &amp; F is some of the posts that go on for a while.  While it's true some of the post goes off into a chat between a couple people, there are still some valid flames in there.  As it is, people don't come here much anymore.  Look at the last 30 or so topics.  They date back to 6 days ago when they were last commented on.  Used to be maybe 1 day before. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ukuwenfallenleaf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>KuwenFallenleaf</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.student.nada.kth.se/~md96-jma/eq/us.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>The Peanut Gallery</span><br>  Posts: 2262<br> <font color=#333333>(4/15/02 9:00:50 am)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.interplay.com/bgate2/images2/mainimage1.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: WTB  a New Board....</span><hr size=1> I thought we got gold for a year last time /shrug if and when it comes up again, despite the heavy moderation, I will donate again to help out. Even though I have my own support tag. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uzjinaar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zjinaar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 151<br> <font color=#333333>(4/15/02 9:01:25 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: WTB  a New Board....</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE